:JOURNEY
Rereading The Kite Runner
Read
Impact
- Childhood chapters | 4 | Devastating twice
- Betrayal scene | 5 | Harder now
- Return to Afghanistan | 5 | More textured | Politically and emotionally richer now
- Final act | 4 | Earned and neat

:NOW
Thinking about what other books I read young would change on a second read \
in middle age. The Kite Runner moved first on my list.

